name: Available Or Leased Shops At Airport
query:
select airport as "Airport",
count(case when status = "Available" then 1 end) as "Available Shop",
count(case when status = "Occupied" then 0 end) as "Leased Shop",
count(name) as "Total Shop"
from `tabShop Details`
group by airport;
report_name: Available Or Leased Shops At Airport
